	<title type="text">Early Years Policies</title>
	<subtitle type="text">Westward is an independent co-educational school for children from nursery age to eleven-plus. Westward enjoys a reputation for traditional standards and high academic achievements which goes hand in hand with development of caring personalities and individuality.</subtitle>
	<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="/"/>
	<id>https://westwardschool.co.uk/index.php/early-years/early-years-policies.feed</id>
	<updated>2016-11-30T17:42:14Z</updated>
